'''威圖公司'''（{{Lang-en|Vertu Corporation}}，[[商業名稱|商業名稱]]：C-MORE系統<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.militaryindustrialcomplex.com/contract_detail.asp?contract_id=19316 |title=Vertu Corporation dba C-More Competition defense contract to the Army given on 4/2/2012 |accessdate=2020-07-27 |archive-date=2020-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726161219/https://www.militaryindustrialcomplex.com/contract_detail.asp?contract_id=19316 |dead-url=no }}</ref>）是一間美國槍械和槍械附件生產商。

== 歷史 ==
1993年，威圖在[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]][[馬納薩斯_(維吉尼亞州)|馬納薩斯獨立市]]成立；<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://dealers.gundigest.com/l/7370/Vertu-Corp |title=Archived copy |access-date=2012-08-12 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130124222534/http://dealers.gundigest.com/l/7370/Vertu-Corp |archive-date=2013-01-24 |url-status=dead |dead-url=no }}</ref>而C-MORE競賽之名則是於1999年成立。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cedhk.com/shop/news/2/US-Army-Awarded-Contract-to-C%252dMORE-Competition.html |title=US Army Awarded Contract to C-MORE Competition |access-date=2012-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120402211554/http://www.cedhk.com/shop/news/2/US-Army-Awarded-Contract-to-C-MORE-Competition.html |archive-date=2012-04-02 |url-status=dead |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 產品 ==
威圖的主要產品是[[紅點鏡|紅點鏡]]，用於各款[[M1911手槍|M1911手槍]]、[[格洛克手槍|格洛克手槍]]和{{Link-en|AR-15樣式步槍|AR-15 style rifle}}。[[埃斯塔勒国营工厂|埃斯塔勒国营工厂]]亦推薦該瞄準鏡用於[[M249班用自動武器|M249班用自動武器]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.fnhusa.com/le/products/firearms/model.asp?fid=FNF014&gid=FNG008&mid=FNM0041 |title=M249 SAW (Squad Automatic Weapon) |access-date=2009-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090328024311/http://www.fnhusa.com/le/products/firearms/model.asp?fid=FNF014&gid=FNG008&mid=FNM0041 |archive-date=2009-03-28 |url-status=dead |dead-url=no }}</ref>和[[M240通用機槍|M240通用機槍]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.fnhusa.com/le/products/firearms/model.asp?fid=FNF015&gid=FNG008&mid=FNM0043 |title=M240 B |accessdate=2020-07-27 |archive-date=2008-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080926185921/http://www.fnhusa.com/le/products/firearms/model.asp?fid=FNF015&gid=FNG008&mid=FNM0043 |dead-url=no }}</ref>該公司還為[[美军|美军]]生產[[M26模組配件霰彈槍系統|M26模組配件霰彈槍系統]]。<ref>{{cite web| url=https://scopeslife.com/bushnell-trs-25-review/| title=Bushnell TRS-25 Guide| accessdate=2020-07-27| archive-date=2019-05-17| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517171118/https://scopeslife.com/bushnell-trs-25-review/| dead-url=no}} Friday, 17 May 2019</ref>

